{"tid":1954280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開] 希望做唔住嘅黃店推出飯券\"預先付款\"","createTime":"2020-04-01T16:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T01:12:18.000Z","uid":101117,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e21ba1414dc83dd7546c4159ca879fcb1108be3d","tid":1954280,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:55:34.000Z","msg":"之前開咗喺飲食台，有巴打建議開喺時事台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃店每日畀人搞鳩<br />\n淋紅油嘅有、畀狗揸住把尺屈唔夠1.5米又有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪應該推出飯券畀大家預先付款<br />\n幫手解決cash flow 嘅燃眉之急 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢段時間真係唔係唔想幫襯<br />\n但係真係寧願唔出街 <br />\n雖然可以嗌Foodpanda <br />\n但入我地址 reach 唔到自己區入面嘅黃店 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考如下: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2TskR4A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2TskR4A.png&h=a0822698&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLink: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kimchifriedinews/photos/a.551126505417357/761039027759436/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkimchifriedinews%2Fphotos%2Fa.551126505417357%2F761039027759436%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=b982d707\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kimchifriedinews/photos/a.551126505417357/761039027759436/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n明白依家成個經濟環境唔好唔係個個有消費力<br />\n但如果有啲黃店可以逆市開分店<br />\n咁其實係咪啫係我地有能力消費只係分唔勻啲資源呢？<br />\n<br />\n我諗都仲有一班有能力消費嘅手足<br />\n不過因為WFH限制太多<br />\n自己區都尚算可以幫下手但跨區真係冇辦法<br />\n飯券係其中一個方法去消除地域上限制<br />\n但真正想做到嘅係分配資源等多啲黃店可以生存到落嚟<br />\n而唔係永遠淨係出名嗰幾間/ 告急完一排啲人就唔記得<br />\n呢樣野可能就需要一樣媒介/ 平台去協調<br />\n<br />\n技術上可唔可以做到黃店眾籌/ gift card 網<br />\n去到某個quota就stop, 其他支持就spare畀另外一啲舖頭呢？<br />\n利申: 9up 乜撚都唔識<br />\n<br />\n咁樣或者可以吸納更多店加入黃色陣營 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實行上唔容易，都要冒住變軍票嘅風險<br />\n但我就覺得運動到依家雖然步步為營但好多時候都講個信字<br />\n見越嚟越多黃店做唔住，又唔太見出面有大Post講<br />\n所以想開個post討論下<br />\n<br />\n食肆自己應該會避嫌唔會自己提出嚟<br />\n討論多啲多啲人支持嘅話先做得起<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌細力啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不完美，可接受，要改善 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583fadd3ad7fcd210e1f7e3cc1c0335e28fcb40c","tid":1954280,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:59:54.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"4e5f5981c08c429064a924163c923272768de22b","tid":1954280,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:00:32.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d7a5d148e436bc679df1e0c76946896543748f6c","tid":1954280,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:00:43.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"5e7d1c0e7eceda61104a1f6c07a3a8d15a0178a5","tid":1954280,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />賣現金券"},{"pid":"e634c180d7af606669482f62aac476f9dff820a0","tid":1954280,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5470bd755a96a4e2d49d83df75466eb58dc03d0b","tid":1954280,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:04:49.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"5f063254b09a055977b6deef84b73236013579e0","tid":1954280,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike"