>\n其實係有，已經有人做左。只係唔多店加盟/登記。<br />\n<br />\n利申：未用過，因為唔肯定有冇伏。"},{"pid":"4642e03f5aa2ba5b3fd70573c717e22773dd8e55","tid":1954280,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:20:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5076de3b1389add87ce365f84f689b073da3c82d","tid":1954280,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:20:16.000Z","msg":"留名幫推"},{"pid":"2db8a0de7d716157c0988b57d1f4f34df03a6fe6","tid":1954280,"uid":101117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8450ee7820ad259d09fd7f71b1d894386d98a470","tid":1954280,"uid":68493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:16:42.000Z","msg":"讚成，不過都要諗下賣完劵都頂唔順咁點算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:21:30.000Z","msg":"冇錯，飯券前提係呢段要捱嘅時間唔太長<br />\n我長期坐住個腦，所以開post等大家一齊諗下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4c3038cff73a99733cd55c9920100d49416430","tid":1954280,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8450ee7820ad259d09fd7f71b1d894386d98a470","tid":1954280,"uid":68493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:16:42.000Z","msg":"讚成，不過都要諗下賣完劵都頂唔順咁點算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:21:51.000Z","msg":"都冇計 呢啲野講唔埋"},{"pid":"88a9a30a54619954aad23fa199f9d3422ceda5e2","tid":1954280,"uid":183194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:22:36.000Z","msg":"黃店做唔掂唔好格硬做，下降週期太長唔見底蝕死，反觀黃陣銘記餓死都唔好幫襯藍店先係重點"},{"pid":"730c928e045e23e493aef848fbeeb83f621c379d","tid":1954280,"uid":23037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f4c3038cff73a99733cd55c9920100d49416430","tid":1954280,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8450ee7820ad259d09fd7f71b1d894386d98a470","tid":1954280,"uid":68493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:16:42.000Z","msg":"讚成，不過都要諗下賣完劵都頂唔順咁點算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:21:51.000Z","msg":"都冇計 呢啲野講唔埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:22:44.0